lead_paragraph: BIENSTOCK--Lillian, on February 2, 2014. Beloved wife of the late Joseph; loving mother of Carole and Ted Rosten; cherished grandmother of Danielle Holzman and Peter Rosten; devoted sister of Dorothy Watnofsky and Gloria Dobbs; devoted aunt and great-aunt.
